item.title: CVE-2021-3834|2024-09-16T17:37:38.171Z -- %C3%A1rtica -- integria%20ims
item.description: Integria IMS in its 5.0.92 version does not filter correctly some fields related to the login.php file. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability in order to perform a cross-site scripting attack (XSS).
